               <msContents>
                  <summary>Pp. 1-2: List of the Books of the Bible and their abbreviations. P. 3: Notice of donation (Hedar 5, 1938) from Emperor Haile Selassie to the National Library, along with mention of several members of the royal family. Commentary on the Four Gospels, አርባዕቱ፡ ወንጌል፡, text and commentary. Pp. 4-16: Introduction to the Four Gospels.  Pp. 16-252: Commentary on the Gospel of Matthew. Pp. 252-363: Commentary on the Gospel of John. Pp. 364-377: Commentary on the Gospel of Mark. Pp. 378-458: Commentary on the Gospel of Luke. Pp. 459: Geneaology of the Royal Line from Adam to Amda Tseyon.  P. 460: Colophon mentioning date, 1913, commissioner, Regent Ras Tafari, Empress Zewditu, place of copying (Gojjam, Nazret, Dabra Iyasus), etc.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="3v" to="127r">Fols 3v–127r</locus>
                     <title>Commentary on the gospel of Matthew</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="am">ይህ ፡ ቃል ፡ የ፫፻ነው ፡ ጥንተ ፡ ነገሩ ፡ እንደምን ፡ ነው ፡ ቢሉ ፡ እግዚአብሔር ፡ እምቅድመ ፡ ዓለም ፡ በልብ ፡ የመከረውን ፡ በነቢያት ፡ ያናገረውን ፡ ለመፈጸም ፡ ሥጋ ፡ ሆነ ፤</incipit>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <locus from="127v" to="183v">Fols 127v–183v</locus>
                     <title>Commentary on the gospel of John</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="am">ይህ ፡ ቃል ፡ የ፫፻ ፡ ነው ፡ ጥንተ ፡ ነገሩ ፡ እንደምን ፡ ብለህ ፡ እንደ ፡ ማቴዎስ ፡ ተርክ ። ከዚህም ፡ ዮሐንስ ፡ እንደ ፡ አባቶቹ ፡ እንደ ፡ ነቢያት ፡ እንደ ፡ ወንድሞቹ ፡ እንደ ፡ ሐዋርያት ፡ አይድፍም ።</incipit>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3">
                     <locus from="184r" to="190v">Fols 184r–190v</locus>
                     <title>Commentary on the gospel of Mark</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="am">ማርቆስ ፡ ማለት ፡ ንህብ ፡ ማለት ፡ ነው ፡ ንህብ ፡ ከሁሉ ፡ እንዲቀስም ፡ እሱም ፡ አስቀድሞ ፡ ከጌታ ፡ ኋላ ፡ ከሐዋርያት ፡ ተምሯልና ።</incipit>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i4">
                     <locus from="191r" to="231r">Fols 191r–231r</locus>
                     <title>Commentary on the gospel of Luke</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="am">ሉቃስ ፡ ማለት ፡ ጠቢብ ፡ ማለት ፡ ነው ። ቀድሞ ፡ ዓቃቤ ፡ ሥራይ ፡ ዘሥጋ ፡ ነበረ ። ኋላ ፡ ዓቃቤ ፡ ሥራይ ፡ ዘነፍስ ፡ ሁደል ።</incipit>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i5">
                     <locus target="#231v">Fol. 231v</locus>
                     <title>Genealogy, From Adam to Emperor Āmda Ṣeyon</title>
                     
                  </msItem>
